parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The disintegration of the dashboard can cause sharp plastic shards to fly into the passenger compartment, potentially causing injuries to the driver and passengers. In the event of an airbag deployment, the sharp plastic shards can be propelled into the face and chest, leading to serious injuries.
symptoms: The dashboard cracks and breaks into sharp pieces
falling into the wiring and electrical components under the dash. The cracks can spread rapidly
causing the dashboard to disintegrate completely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hood latch can cause the hood to fly open while driving, obstructing the driver's view and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The hood latch breaks or fails
causing the hood to open suddenly while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle loses power
the transmission fails to engage
the vehicle stalls or hesitates when shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power train can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or stalls when shifting gears
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle loses power
the drive shaft breaks or fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the dashboard and interior components can cause distractions, discomfort, and safety concerns for the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The dashboard cracks or breaks
the interior components fail or malfunction
the driver's seat moves or malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical and ignition systems can cause the vehicle to stall, hesitate, or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or hesitates
the electrical system malfunctions
the ignition system fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The "death wobble" can cause the driver to lose control of the vehicle, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Violent shaking or wobbling of the front end
loss of steering control
and difficulty braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Steering Column and Steering Gear Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the steering column or gear can cause loss of steering control, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Sudden loss of steering control
difficulty turning
and unusual noises or vibrations from the steering system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the airbag system or dashboard can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Cracking or crumbling of the dashboard
airbag deployment issues
and failure of the airbag system to deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the power steering system can cause loss of steering control, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Difficulty steering
unusual noises or vibrations from the power steering system
and loss of power steering assist.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the frame or suspension can cause loss of control, accidents, or near-misses, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Unusual noises or vibrations from the suspension
difficulty steering
and loss of control.
